- They say "a picture is worth a thousand words" but just how many calories?  Well now you can find out!
- Take photos of your foods and meals using the camera. FatSecret uses image recognition to try and identify the foods in the photo so you can easily add them to your food diary
- Join the #Photodiet #Foodsnap #Instacalorie revolution

This update greatly improves the functionality of the diet weight tracker.  
- Delete weigh in entries
- Edit weigh in entries
- Change the starting date of your diet
- Rotate the phone to view your complete weight history chart

Thanks for sharing your amazing experiences using food image recognition to help you calorie count - we love it!  Get around the #Photodiet with FatSecret #Foodsnap and join our #Instacalorie revolution.

The FatSecret team wish you great health and happiness. Together we can help achieve your diet and weight loss goals.

- Greatly improved and simplified app navigation with a new menu so you can get around the app much faster. 
- There’s also a fantastic new home screen showcasing the best content from the FatSecret community. 
- If you want to see your photos featured, make sure you visit “Settings” within the App, and change your sharing to “with everyone”.
- You can always go back to the classic menu and home screen if you prefer from settings.

- Buddies has been updated to a follower/following relationship which continues to respect your privacy settings
- Share your journal, weigh-ins and food entries with others who follow you to get encouragement and support. Be inspired by others you follow
- App now remembers your last screen viewed, even if you don’t use it for several days
- App also remembers your feed filter setting on the community feed on Home

Premium subscriptions are now available for enhanced features to help you achieve your diet and weight management goals
 - Meal Planning: plan what you’ll eat weeks in advance and know your calorie and macro targets before you start
 - Custom Meal headings: add up to six additional meal types throughout the day
 - Water Tracking: make sure you reach a daily water intake goal
